column5: Going to this lodge for the first time in early june. Never fished this lake. Any help on the fishing would be a great help. I mainly fish pike, but help with walleye fishing would be great too! Thanks Big Rob

Going to this lodge for the first time in early june. Never fished this lake. Any help on the fishing would be a great help. I mainly fish pike, but help with walleye fishing would be great too! Thanks Big Rob

I fished the lake for several years but havn't been there for 15 years. There have been several threads on this lake in the past few months. Do a search and plug in Nungesser Lake and you'll pick up some good information.
Hi Fished Nungesser two years ago first week in July. caught plenty of 22-25 in walleyes. Did not persue pike. Would go back again
